data.description: Beautiful New Construction (2023) - INCOME PRODUCING PROPERTY! This property is excellent to live in one, and rent the other to generate income, or buy it as an investment. It is a duplex, each one has 3 bedrooms, two bathrooms, kitchen, dining room and a garage built in 2023! This Cozy Duplex has an Open Floor Concepts which features a Large Kitchen with Soft Close Cabinets, NEW dishwasher, GRANITE Counter Tops/Matching Granite Vanities, Breakfast Bar and NEW Stainless-Steel appliances. Brand NEW washer and dryer. Enjoy your Privacy with a Covered Patio a NEW FENCE between units. 10yr Warranty! The proximity to I-95 allows for easy commuting, while the nearby shopping, NICE dining options cater to your daily needs, parks, schools, Palm Coast Town Center and Entertainment. Plus, with just a few minutes' drive, you can reach the beautiful beaches, perfect for a relaxation in the Florida Sun. Don't miss out on this OPPORTUNITY! Schedule your Private Tour Today!
